               <p>- Shipton depos'd, That Wilmer brought two of the Hats to him to sell.</p>
               <p>It appear'd by the Evidence, That the Prisoners were Idle Boys, and us'd to lie in the Glass-House, and liv'd by Pilfering. And the Fact being plainly prov'd, the Jury found them both <rs id="t17310224-37-verdict191" type="verdictDescription">
